          {
            t({
              en: "Southwark Council's Free Booklet",
              es: "Folleto gratuito del Ayuntamiento de Southwark",
            })
          }
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-8xl mx-auto mb-6">
          {
            t({
              en: "Download a free downloadable booklet with more information about the Latin Ageing UK C.I.C - as well as other organisations and services in Southwark that support healthy ageing for residents aged 50+.",
